Health Minister Zweli Mkhize along with the health MECs are detailing Phase 2 of the National Vaccine Rollout. Courtesy #DStv403 * Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - Health Minister Zweli Mkhize along with health MECs are detailing Phase 2 of the National Vaccine Rollout. The second phase of the rollout is scheduled to start on Monday. Health authorities say only those who have registered and received an SMS confirming an appointment should go to a vaccination centre.